<br>level 40-49  entry: 250pp  1st prize 2500pp<br>level 50-60  entry: 500pp  1st prize 5000pp<br><br>I am looking for a minimum of 10 in each category to award the proper prizes.  If more enter, the prizes will be greater and prizes for 2nd and 3rd place can be awarded.  I welcome any questions or suggestions you might have.  But I will not provide every detail of the event until right before it happens.  There will be rules to follow, so pay close attention to this post and others like it.  Send tells to Straughn, Lojitsu, or Tracedar online as well if you're interested.<br><br>Well met all,<br><br>Straughn, Rogue of the 18th backstab<br>Tracedar, Ranger of the 19th search<br>Lojitsu, Monk of the 11th prayer  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulojitsu1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lojitsu1</A> at: 8/14/02 9:52:12 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#403C50><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulojitsu1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lojitsu1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/9/02 5:28:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm70.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://home.attbi.com/~eqmaximus/brell/post9.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Come Join the TRANSCONTINENTAL HUNT</span><hr size=1> Update:<br><br>I have completed hunts for category I and II (levels 1-9 and 10-19).  Send tells if you are interested....I will schedule these soon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#464446><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulojitsu1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lojitsu1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/13/02 9:35:49 am)</font><br>  